11
00:01:32,485 --> 00:01:36,251
We came for a memorial service.
Not to go skiing.

12
00:01:36,656 --> 00:01:38,920
Mama, you also want to ski, right?

13
00:01:41,996 --> 00:01:45,591
0h, I want to ski!
I'm dying to ski!

14
00:01:46,635 --> 00:01:49,103
I can't wait to see Yoshimi.

15
00:01:49,272 --> 00:01:52,139
Spring vacation's great.
No homework.

16
00:02:00,552 --> 00:02:03,248
I thought you grew out of that.

17
00:02:03,488 --> 00:02:04,785
My lucky charm.

18
00:02:05,825 --> 00:02:09,226
It's so cute...
Give it to me.

19
00:02:09,395 --> 00:02:10,225
Nope.

20
00:03:07,163 --> 00:03:08,323
Look out!

21
00:03:46,643 --> 00:03:49,203
Heisuke Sugita
Naoko
Monami

22
